// intelligence.proto — Connect-RPC contract for the AI-coach layer that
// turns Hone into a personal coach. Two RPCs:
//
//   GetDailyBrief — synthesised "morning brief" derived from focus stats,
//                   skipped/completed plan items, recent reflections and
//                   recently-touched notes. Cached 6h per (user, date);
//                   force=true bypasses cache (rate-limited 1/h).
//
//   AskNotes      — RAG over the user's notes corpus. Embed question →
//                   cosine top-8 → LLM answer with [N] citations parsed
//                   into structured payload.
//
// Bounded context: this service READS from hone_* tables via reader
// adapters (focus, plan, notes) and WRITES only to its own
// hone_daily_briefs table. It must never mutate hone domain tables.

